:: Pot Sage TF Complete|en-US [twee]
<<set $outside to 0>><<set $location to "school">><<schooleffects>><<effects>>
<<npc Sage>><<person1>>

The moment you step into the lab, Sage rushes over, clutching a vial of faintly glowing liquid.
<br><br>
"I did it! I mapped the chemical mechanism behind these changes!" <<he>> says, almost breathless. "I can't fully reverse it—"
<br><br>
Sage's voice dips suddenly, as if a hand has pressed down on the sound itself. <<He>> stares past you, eyes fixed on something that isn't there.
"That belongs to..."
<br><br>
The next word never quite arrives. It twists into a dry hiss, like radio static with no radio, leaving only an aftertaste of meaning—something your mind refuses to hold.
<br><br>
A sudden chill crawls up your spine. The lights seem to dim for a heartbeat, and the air prickles with a faint, impossible charge. Who—or what—was Sage about to name?
<br><br>
"Ahem. Anyway," Sage blinks hard, snapping back to normal. "Now that we're brushing against the edge of what matter can be... I can synthesise compounds to <b>accelerate</b> or <b>inhibit</b> the process."
<br><br>
<<he>> gestures at a neat row of labelled bottles. "If you ever need to adjust your condition, come to me."
<br><br>
<<set $Pot.sageEventStage to 3>>
<<npcincr Sage love 5>><<gglove Sage>>
<br>
<<Llink "Browse potion services" "Pot Sage TF Shop">><</Llink>>
<br>
<<Llink "Common.Back" "Pot ChemLab">><<endevent>><</Llink>>

