:: Pot Sage TF Potion|en-US [twee]
<<set $outside to 0>><<set $location to "school">><<schooleffects>><<effects>>

You drink the potion.
<br>

<<if $potionMode is "inhibitor">>
	<<if $potionType is "wolf">>
		A chill slides down your throat, like winter wind mixed with the bitterness of silver needle grass. The restlessness inside you calms down.
	<<elseif $potionType is "cat">>
		It tastes like over-steeped peppermint tea, leaving a numbing sensation on your tongue. The urge to scratch fades away.
	<<elseif $potionType is "cow">>
		It tastes like concentrated herbal juice without sugar, bitter and earthy. Your body feels less heavy and heated.
	<<elseif $potionType is "bird">>
		It feels like swallowing liquid lead, weighing down the lightness that urges you to fly. A taste of stale seeds lingers in your mouth.
	<<elseif $potionType is "fox">>
		Extremely bitter, like biting into an unripe acorn. The constant urge to play pranks is forcibly suppressed.
	<<else>>
		It tastes like unripe lemon mixed with mint.
	<</if>>
	<br><br>
	<<transform $potionType -10>>
	<span class="blue">You feel that wild edge inside you recede.</span>
<<else>>
	<<if $potionType is "wolf">>
		Spicy! The liquid burns down your esophagus, filling your mouth with the taste of rust and raw meat. You have a sudden urge to howl at the moon.
	<<elseif $potionType is "cat">>
		Like warm melted butter mixed with strong catnip, sweet enough to make you dizzy. Your fingertips itch, and your pupils contract involuntarily.
	<<elseif $potionType is "cow">>
		A rich sweetness, blending the scent of fresh alfalfa and warm milk. You feel a warm current rushing to your chest and belly.
	<<elseif $potionType is "bird">>
		A crisp sweet-and-sour taste, like a handful of bursting wild berries. You feel as if a light breeze is trying to lift you up.
	<<elseif $potionType is "fox">>
		Sickly sweet with a hint of smoky burnt wood. Drinking it gives you a strange sense of excitement and cunning.
	<<else>>
		It tastes spicy and stimulating, like a fire burning in your stomach.
	<</if>>
	<br><br>
	<<transform $potionType 10>>
	<span class="purple">You feel the wildness inside you flare!</span>
<</if>>

<br><br>
<<Llink "Common.Back" "Pot ChemLab">><<endevent>><</Llink>>
